{"tid":1591941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"內心掙扎同矛盾","createTime":"2019-09-24T11:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T11:24:21.000Z","uid":323700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29df7ca3ce0888dfe17dd61117e53c58af27838f","tid":1591941,"uid":323700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"我不是前線<br />\n我無勇氣當前線<br />\n但是2019年我踏出了和理非的第一步<br />\n我在2019年開始覺得自己是一個真正的香港人<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己無資格去指責人<br />\n但係我覺得到左2019如果身為和理非但係仍然一次遊行都唔出來既人<br />\n重有無資格叫自己做和理非?<br />\n<br />\n咁多老人家隨時一命嗚呼都願意上街遊行<br />\n就算只係嗌幾句口號<br />\n但係點解咁多&quot;和理非&quot;既年輕人<br />\n重可以比藉口自己淨係做冷氣軍師?<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想分化<br />\n我只係有好多野諗唔明<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd2b7238989c7a850fb6f772bae61286d6f9006","tid":1591941,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"}]}